---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AxionFlow - Engineering First. AI Second.">
	<nav class="border-b border-white/10 bg-[#0F1115]/80 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
				<img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/img/logo-menor.png`} alt="AxionFlow" class="h-8 w-auto" />
				<span class="font-mono font-bold text-lg tracking-tight">AxionFlow</span>
			</div>
			
			<div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-white/60">
				<a href="#audit" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Audit</a>
				<a href="#architecture" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Architecture</a>
				<a href="#philosophy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Philosophy</a>
			</div>

			<div>
				<a href="mailto:professional_inquiry@axionflow.com" class="bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-mono transition-colors">
					SYSTEM_CHECK
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<main>
		<!-- HERO SECTION -->
		<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 px-6 border-b border-white/5">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="max-w-3xl">
					<h1 class="font-mono text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-8">
						Engineering First.<br/>
						<span class="text-white/40">AI Second.</span>
					</h1>
					
					<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/60 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed mb-12">
						We build, audit, and repair production LLM systems.
						No magic. No prompt engineering hype. Just strict, deterministic pipelines.
					</p>

					<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
						<a href="mailto:professional_inquiry@axionflow.com" class="bg-[#3B82F6] hover:bg-[#2563EB] text-white px-8 py-4 font-mono font-bold text-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-colors">
							[ SCHEDULE AUDIT ]
						</a>
						<a href="https://github.com/KerubinDev/AxionFlow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white px-8 py-4 font-mono text-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-colors">
							View Engine Code ↗
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- REALITY CHECK SECTION -->
		<section class="py-24 px-6 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#0F1115]">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-white/10 border border-white/10">
					<!-- Card 1 -->
					<div class="bg-[#0F1115] p-8 md:p-12">
						<div class="font-mono text-[#F59E0B] text-sm mb-4">01 // THE BLACK BOX PROBLEM</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono">Unpredictable Wrappers</h3>
						<p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
							Most "AI features" are unpredictable wrappers around API calls. You don't know why they fail, you can't replay errors, and you can't guarantee safety.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Card 2 -->
					<div class="bg-[#0F1115] p-8 md:p-12">
						<div class="font-mono text-[#F59E0B] text-sm mb-4">02 // TECH DEBT VELOCITY</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono">Unverified Code</h3>
						<p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
							Generated code is often unverified code. Without a rigid validation layer, your team is merging bugs faster than they can write tests.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Card 3 -->
					<div class="bg-[#0F1115] p-8 md:p-12">
						<div class="font-mono text-[#F59E0B] text-sm mb-4">03 // COMPLIANCE & RISK</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono">Legal Exposure</h3>
						<p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
							If you can't trace exactly why the model took an action, you can't use it in regulated environments. "The AI did it" is not a legal defense.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- PHILOSOPHY SECTION -->
		<section id="philosophy" class="py-24 px-6 border-b border-white/5">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
				<div>
					<h2 class="font-mono text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">We don't fix code with "Chat". <span class="text-white/40">We fix it with Pipelines.</span></h2>
					<p class="text-lg text-white/60 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
						We reject the idea of the "chatbot assistant". Production-grade AI requires a Software Engineering approach.
					</p>
					
					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="font-mono text-[#3B82F6] font-bold">01.</div>
							<div>
								<h4 class="font-bold mb-1 font-mono">Analyze</h4>
								<p class="text-sm text-white/60">Deep AST parsing of your existing codebase.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="font-mono text-[#3B82F6] font-bold">02.</div>
							<div>
								<h4 class="font-bold mb-1 font-mono">Plan</h4>
								<p class="text-sm text-white/60">Deterministic step-by-step implementation plans (Markdown).</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="font-mono text-[#3B82F6] font-bold">03.</div>
							<div>
								<h4 class="font-bold mb-1 font-mono">Execute</h4>
								<p class="text-sm text-white/60">Generation of standardUnified Diffs (not direct mutations).</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-4">
							<div class="font-mono text-[#3B82F6] font-bold">04.</div>
							<div>
								<h4 class="font-bold mb-1 font-mono">Validate</h4>
								<p class="text-sm text-white/60">Mandatory local builds, tests, and linting before merge.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-8 font-mono text-sm overflow-hidden">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
						<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
						<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
						<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
						<div class="ml-4 text-white/40">pipeline.log</div>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2 text-white/80">
						<div class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400">➜</span> <span>Analyze: Parsing project structure...</span></div>
						<div class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">✓</span> <span>Found 14 source files</span></div>
						<div class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400">➜</span> <span>Plan: Generative architectural review...</span></div>
						<div class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">✓</span> <span>Plan generated: implementation_plan.md</span></div>
						<div class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#F59E0B]">⚠</span> <span>Review required: Breaking change detected</span></div>
						<div class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400">➜</span> <span>Execute: Applying diffs...</span></div>
						<div class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">✓</span> <span>3 files modified</span></div>
						<div class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400">➜</span> <span>Validate: Running test suite...</span></div>
						<div class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-green-500">✓</span> <span>Tests passed (42/42)</span></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- SERVICES SECTION -->
		<section id="services" class="py-24 px-6 bg-[#0F1115]">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
					<!-- Service 1 -->
					<div id="audit" class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 md:p-12 hover:border-[#3B82F6]/50 transition-colors group">
						<div class="font-mono text-[#3B82F6] text-sm mb-6 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">> OFFER_01: SYSTEM AUDIT</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 font-mono">Technical Traceability Audit</h3>
						<p class="text-white/60 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
							We reverse-engineer your current LLM implementation to identify non-deterministic behaviors and security gaps.
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-3 font-mono text-sm text-white/80 border-t border-white/10 pt-6">
							<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">+</span> Vulnerability Report</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">+</span> Deterministic Trace Map</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">+</span> Risk Assessment Field Guide</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<!-- Service 2 -->
					<div id="architecture" class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-8 md:p-12 hover:border-[#3B82F6]/50 transition-colors group">
						<div class="font-mono text-[#3B82F6] text-sm mb-6 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">> OFFER_02: ARCHITECTURE DESIGN</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 font-mono">Pipeline Architecture</h3>
						<p class="text-white/60 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
							We design and build the orchestration layer for your product using AxionFlow principles. Fully containerized and strict.
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-3 font-mono text-sm text-white/80 border-t border-white/10 pt-6">
							<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">+</span> Custom Orchestration Engine</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">+</span> Tool Definition & Security</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">+</span> Local-First CI/CD Integration</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ENGINE SECTION -->
		<section class="py-24 px-6 border-y border-white/5">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="bg-[#0F1115] border border-white/10 p-8 md:p-16 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#3B82F6]/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
					
					<h2 class="font-mono text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">POWERED BY AXIONFLOW</h2>
					<p class="text-white/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
						Our methodology isn't theoretical. It's built on <strong>AxionFlow</strong>, our open-source orchestration engine.
						We don't sell proprietary lock-in. We build on transparent tooling.
					</p>
					
					<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 font-mono text-sm text-[#3B82F6] mb-12">
						<span>[ Open Source MIT ]</span>
						<span>[ Local-First ]</span>
						<span>[ Audit-Native ]</span>
					</div>

					<a href="https://github.com/KerubinDev/AxionFlow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white hover:text-[#3B82F6] transition-colors border-b border-white/20 hover:border-[#3B82F6] pb-1">
						Explore the Repository ↗
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- TECHNICAL LEAD SECTION -->
		<section class="py-24 px-6 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#0F1115]">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="border-l-2 border-[#3B82F6] pl-6 md:pl-10">
					<div class="font-mono text-[#3B82F6] text-sm mb-4">TECHNICAL OWNERSHIP</div>
					<h2 class="font-mono text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Built by Engineers, for Engineers.</h2>
					<p class="text-xl text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-8">
						AxionFlow was born from a refusal to accept non-deterministic behavior in production software. I designed this engine to replace "prompt engineering" guesswork with verifiable structural analysis.
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-10">
						I assume technical responsibility for the rigorous standards this tool enforces. It is not a toy; it is an infrastructure component for serious engineering teams.
					</p>
					
					<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-mono font-bold text-[#3B82F6]">
							K
						</div>
						<div>
							<div class="font-mono font-bold text-white">Kelvin</div>
							<div class="text-sm text-white/40">Principal Engineer & Architect</div>
						</div>
						<div class="ml-auto flex gap-4 text-sm text-white/40 font-mono">
							<a href="https://github.com/KerubinDev" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">GitHub ↗</a>
							<a href="mailto:professional_inquiry@axionflow.com" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Email ↗</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<section class="py-32 px-6 text-center">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-mono text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 tracking-tight">READY TO STABILIZE YOUR INTELLIGENCE?</h2>
				<p class="text-xl text-white/40 mb-12 font-light">Stop gambling with probability. Start engineering with certainty.</p>
				
				<a href="mailto:professional_inquiry@axionflow.com" class="inline-block bg-[#EAEAEA] text-[#0F1115] hover:bg-white px-10 py-5 font-mono font-bold text-lg transition-colors">
					[ EMAIL ENGINEERING TEAM ]
				</a>
				<div class="mt-6 text-sm font-mono text-white/30">
					professional_inquiry@axionflow.com
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<footer class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-white/5 text-sm text-white/40">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
				<span class="font-mono font-bold text-white/60">AxionFlow</span>
				<span>© 2026</span>
			</div>
			<div class="flex gap-8">
				<a href="https://github.com/KerubinDev/AxionFlow" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">GitHub</a>
				<a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Legal</a>
				<a href="mailto:contact@axionflow.com" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>
</Layout>
